OL,3,CArthur's Seat blaze extinguished as
OL,4,Cwildfire warnings continue across
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FA fire at Arthur's Seat in Edinburgh
OL,8,Fhas been extinguished after burning
OL,9,Ffor three days, but the risk of
OL,10,Fwildfires across Scotland remains high.
OL,12,FEmergency services were called to
OL,13,Freports of a grassfire at 6.30pm on
OL,14,FSunday evening, the Scottish Fire and
OL,15,FRescue Service (SFRS) said.
OL,17,FResidents were told to keep windows
OL,18,Fand doors shut and avoid the area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
