OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784679493
OL,3,CArthur's Seat blaze extinguished as
OL,4,Cwildfire warnings continue across
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FOn Monday six fire appliances
OL,8,Fcontinued to tackle the blaze and
OL,9,Fcrews eventually managed to put it out
OL,10,Fat 1pm on Tuesday.
OL,12,FQueen's Drive is now open after being
OL,13,Fclosed for two days, and the SFRS said
OL,14,Fit will continue to monitor the scene.
OL,16,FArea commander David Dourley, said:
OL,17,F"Our crews remained on scene until
OL,18,Ftoday, working to extinguish remaining
OL,19,Fhotspots and dampen down the area.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
