OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784679493
OL,3,CArthur's Seat blaze extinguished as
OL,4,Cwildfire warnings continue across
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,F"I would like to thank all of our
OL,8,Fcrews for their work and our partners
OL,9,Ffor their support. I would also like
OL,10,Fto thank the public for their patience
OL,11,Fand understanding."
OL,13,FA high risk wildfire warning has been
OL,14,Fissued by Scottish Fire and Rescue
OL,15,FService for Central Highlands,
OL,16,FSouthern and Eastern Scotland until
OL,17,FFriday, July 24.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@SO]
