OL,3,CArthur's Seat blaze extinguished as
OL,4,Cwildfire warnings continue across
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FIn the Cairngorms National Park more
OL,8,Fthan 100 firefighters and specialist
OL,9,Fwildfire units are still battling a
OL,10,Fblaze which has been burning since
OL,11,FWednesday.
OL,13,FSRFS said it has deployed helicopters
OL,14,Fto drop water bombs and are drawing
OL,15,Fwater from Loch Morlich via a "high-
OL,16,Fvolume pump," but hotspots remain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
