OL,3,CArthur's Seat blaze extinguished as
OL,4,Cwildfire warnings continue across
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FTen square kilometres of land has been
OL,8,Faffected across the Glenmore and
OL,9,FAbernathy regions and operational
OL,10,Fpresence is expected throughout the
OL,11,Fweek.
OL,13,FGlenmore Forest Park and Loch Morlich
OL,14,Fremains closed to the public and
OL,15,Fvehicles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
