OL,3,CArthur's Seat blaze extinguished as
OL,4,Cwildfire warnings continue across
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FSFRS assistant chief officer Jon
OL,8,FHenderson said: "Although we have made
OL,9,Fsubstantial progress, this remains a
OL,10,Flive operational incident and
OL,11,Ffirefighters will remain in attendance
OL,12,Funtil the area is safe.
OL,14,F"We continue to ask the public to
OL,15,Favoid the area, respect all road
OL,16,Fclosures and cordons, and follow the
OL,17,Fadvice of emergency services at all
OL,18,Ftimes."
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
