OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784679493
OL,3,CArthur's Seat blaze extinguished as
OL,4,Cwildfire warnings continue across
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FHenderson asked people to "not light
OL,8,Fcampfires, use disposable barbecues or
OL,9,Fhave any naked flames near dry
OL,10,Fvegetation."
OL,12,F"It only takes a small spark to start
OL,13,Fa wildfire that can spread rapidly and
OL,14,Fhave a significant impact on
OL,15,Fcommunities, wildlife and the
OL,16,Fenvironment," he explained.
OL,18,FScottish First Minister John Swinney
OL,19,Fthanked the emergency services for
OL,20,Ffighting the Cairngorms wildfire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
