OL,3,CArthur's Seat blaze extinguished as
OL,4,Cwildfire warnings continue across
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FIn a visit to the site, he said: "The
OL,8,Fscale of the wildfire in the
OL,9,FCairngorms is a stark reminder of how
OL,10,Fquickly fires can spread."
OL,12,FHe urged people to be "vigilant" and
OL,13,Fcheck areas for wildfire risks.
